subject: Baseball
lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES, Sept. 12 (AP) — The Dodgers will celebrate the 50th anniversary of their move from Brooklyn to Los Angeles in 2008 with a float in the Rose Parade and a star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame.
